Subject: [PATCH 2/3] frontend/missing-fallback: clean up unused imports in
 broken state

Remove ErrorBoundary import and logProductionError function that were
causing TypeScript build errors. The broken state should build successfully
but show white screens at runtime when component errors occur (because
no error boundary is wrapping the app).
